### Test Categories Endpoints
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/api/v1

### 1. Get All Categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Get Specific Category (ID: 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/1
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Get Category Statistics (Last 30 Days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/1/stats?days=30
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Get Category Statistics (Last 90 Days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/1/stats?days=90
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. Get Non-existent Category (Should return 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/999
Content-Type: application/json

